         MACRO                                                          00160000
.*                                                                      00170000
.* WTO with remote text                                                 00180000
.*                                                                      00190000
&LABEL   RWTO  &TEXT                   * Text for WTO                   00200000
.*                                                                      00210000
.* &LABEL specifies an optional label                                   00220000
.* &TEXT  specifies the text for the WTO. Must specify one of the       00230000
.*        following:                                                    00240000
.*        - Literal text, enclosed in apostrophes                       00250000
.*        - Fieldname of the field containing the parmlist (MAPWTOPL)   00260000
.*        - (reg) pointing to the parmlist (MAPWTOPL)                   00270000
.*                                                                      00280000
.********************************************************************** 00281001
.*                                                                      00282001
.*       IMPORTANT NOTICE                                               00283001
.*       ========= ======                                               00284001
.*                                                                      00285001
